254
00:13:17.958 --> 00:13:19.628
You don't think it's bad. do you?

255
00:13:19.833 --> 00:13:22.963
I don't ever watch TV.
so. you know. I can't tell.

256
00:13:30.333 --> 00:13:31.293
Uh-huh.

257
00:13:32.083 --> 00:13:34.833
I told Henry I'd come out to LA
in two weeks to see him.

258
00:13:38.333 --> 00:13:39.253
Yes?

259
00:13:40.416 --> 00:13:41.286
Nothing.

260
00:13:43.458 --> 00:13:45.328
I can tell you want to give me a note.

261
00:13:45.416 --> 00:13:46.286
No. I don't.

262
00:13:48.333 --> 00:13:52.333
Yeah... I mean. yes. I do. but I guess...

263
00:13:54.375 --> 00:13:56.915
