and once with you.

332
00:17:34.416 --> 00:17:36.246
because I wouldn't mind
going twice anyway.

333
00:17:36.333 --> 00:17:38.133
[Nicole] No. we'll all go together.
sweetheart.

334
00:17:38.208 --> 00:17:41.538
Did you know that Universal Studios
is where I did my first screen test?

335
