before the plants invaded.

363
00:18:55.708 --> 00:18:56.918
I say that with respect.

364
00:18:57.000 --> 00:18:58.460
I was raised by two mothers.

365
00:18:59.000 --> 00:19:01.880
Can you lower the board please. Pablo?

366
00:19:03.208 --> 00:19:05.078
Here? How about here?

367
00:19:06.250 --> 00:19:08.330
- How about now?
- Why is there always a flirty grip?

368
00:19:08.416 --> 00:19:10.706
I can do anything you want.
I just need her here two hours...

369
00:19:10.791 --> 00:19:11.711
Can I say something?

370
00:19:11.791 --> 00:19:13.671
Dennis. hold on. What. honey?

371
00:19:14.166 --> 00:19:15.956
[Nicole] She has to know
how to hold a baby.

372
00:19:16.041 --> 00:19:18.421
- Later on. after she kills Donny...
- [woman] She kills Donny?

373
00:19:18.500 --> 00:19:20.540
That's a secret.
We didn't give the crew those pages.

374
00:19:20.625 --> 00:19:23.035
She becomes a sort of a Earth mother
to the plant community.

375
00:19:23.125 --> 00:19:24.665
That's not going to make any sense

376
00:19:24.750 --> 00:19:26.710
