418
00:21:06.125 --> 00:21:06.955
Oh.

419
00:21:07.250 --> 00:21:08.670
You and Dennis are divorced?

420
00:21:08.750 --> 00:21:09.880
Since 2013.

421
00:21:09.958 --> 00:21:11.168
You still work together.

422
00:21:11.625 --> 00:21:12.535
That's nice.

423
00:21:12.625 --> 00:21:14.035
Oh. no. he's a fucking cocksucker.

