429
00:21:25.500 --> 00:21:26.380
Call Nora.

430
00:21:27.291 --> 00:21:28.581
She saved my life.

431
00:21:30.083 --> 00:21:30.923
Sorry. I...

432
00:21:31.333 --> 00:21:32.293
look so schleppy.

433
00:21:32.375 --> 00:21:34.285
I had an event at my kid's school.

434
00:21:35.416 --> 00:21:36.786
