435
00:21:36.875 --> 00:21:39.205
I think you're a wonderful actress.

436
00:21:39.916 --> 00:21:40.746
Thank you.

437
00:21:40.833 --> 00:21:42.583
I loved All Over The Girl.

438
00:21:42.666 --> 00:21:45.076
but the theater stuff too...

439
00:21:45.166 --> 00:21:46.326
You saw the theater stuff?

440
00:21:46.416 --> 00:21:48.626
I was in New York last year for my book.

441
00:21:49.000 --> 00:21:50.710
which. remind me to give you a copy.

442
00:21:51.125 --> 00:21:52.575
