450
00:22:05.541 --> 00:22:06.381
Hmm.

451
00:22:06.750 --> 00:22:08.330
Well. without me. of course.

452
00:22:08.833 --> 00:22:10.173
He was lucky to have you.

453
00:22:12.833 --> 00:22:13.883
How are you doing?

454
00:22:21.875 --> 00:22:23.495
- [sad chuckle] Sorry.
- [Nora] Oh.

455
00:22:25.041 --> 00:22:25.881
Honey...

456
00:22:25.958 --> 00:22:26.958
[sniffles]

457
00:22:27.041 --> 00:22:28.131
[sighs]

458
00:22:29.208 --> 00:22:30.078
[cries]

459
00:22:30.166 --> 00:22:30.996
[sniffles]

460
00:22:31.083 --> 00:22:32.043
[sighs]

461
00:22:35.541 --> 00:22:36.881
