476
00:23:12.041 --> 00:23:13.381
Oh. good.

477
00:23:14.875 --> 00:23:16.245
Well. Charlie's not terrible.

478
00:23:16.333 --> 00:23:17.673
No. of course not.

479
00:23:18.083 --> 00:23:21.333
But they ravish you with attention
