I'm sure of it.

1044
00:48:02.083 --> 00:48:03.253
But Nicole's not going to lie.

1045
00:48:03.333 --> 00:48:06.213
Listen. if we start from a place
of reasonable.

1046
00:48:06.291 --> 00:48:08.581
