1114
00:50:53.375 --> 00:50:55.285
Just make sure
everything doesn't go to hell.

1115
00:50:55.375 --> 00:50:56.455
- [sighs]
- [phone vibrates]

1116
00:50:56.541 --> 00:50:58.541
- I'm relying on you. okay?
- Fine.

1117
00:50:58.625 --> 00:51:01.205
- Thanks.
- I wish you'd accept generosity better.

1118
00:51:01.291 --> 00:51:02.541
Uh. hold on. Let me...

1119
