1121
00:51:06.333 --> 00:51:08.133
[Nora] Hi. this is Nora Fanshaw.

1122
00:51:08.208 --> 00:51:10.078
I represent your wife. Nicole Barber.

1123
00:51:10.166 --> 00:51:12.246
