1132
00:51:31.916 --> 00:51:33.706
By law. you're meant to respond
within 30 days.

1133
00:51:33.791 --> 00:51:35.251
I didn't like the first lawyer I met.

1134
00:51:35.333 --> 00:51:37.793
[Nora] It says that very clearly
on the document you were given.

1135
00:51:37.875 --> 00:51:38.745
Did you read it?

1136
00:51:38.833 --> 00:51:40.583
Yeah. but I thought
that's just what it says.

1137
00:51:40.666 --> 00:51:42.416
We weren't even going to do it
with lawyers.

1138
00:51:42.500 --> 00:51:43.330
