1205
00:54:38.458 --> 00:54:40.038
- [Henry] I'm going to be rich!
- Okay.

1206
00:54:40.125 --> 00:54:42.285
You're going to go with your daddy.
it's going to be fun.

1207
00:54:42.375 --> 00:54:45.625
And I've got a present for you
