1208
00:54:46.500 --> 00:54:47.670
He's not going to the dentist.

1209
00:54:47.750 --> 00:54:49.710
- I'm trying to help.
- I'm staying here.

1210
00:54:49.791 --> 00:54:50.631
Come on.

1211
00:54:54.625 --> 00:54:55.455
Henry?

1212
00:55:01.083 --> 00:55:03.583
- [Nicole] Got the booster?
- [Charlie] I have a booster.

1213
00:55:05.375 --> 00:55:06.995
Oh. wait. no. it's not in.

1214
00:55:07.375 --> 00:55:08.245
What's not in?

1215
00:55:08.708 --> 00:55:10.708
The seat's not connected.

1216
00:55:13.833 --> 00:55:15.503
