1217
00:55:15.583 --> 00:55:18.333
Yeah. I think they can't
for liability reasons.

1218
00:55:18.583 --> 00:55:20.753
- Do you know how these things...
- Let me just... If you...

1219
00:55:20.833 --> 00:55:23.543
- There should be a clip to clip onto.
