1511
01:07:09.791 --> 01:07:11.131
And I don't like Poppy.

1512
01:07:11.583 --> 01:07:12.963
Here. I have Axel.

1513
01:07:13.041 --> 01:07:15.791
Axel's hilarious.
I think you'd like him. Dad.

1514
01:07:16.791 --> 01:07:18.171
And my family's here.

1515
