1523
01:08:53.416 --> 01:08:54.286
Lift the seat.

1524
01:08:56.333 --> 01:08:57.503
[continues urinating]

1525
01:09:00.666 --> 01:09:02.746
I'm going to have to go back to New York
on Monday.

1526
01:09:03.250 --> 01:09:04.290
Did you flush?

1527
01:09:07.083 --> 01:09:08.083
[toilet flushes]

1528
01:09:08.500 --> 01:09:09.330
[Charlie grunts]

1529
01:09:11.083 --> 01:09:12.043
Wash your hands.

1530
01:09:13.750 --> 01:09:15.290
[Henry] Will you play with me?

1531
01:09:15.375 --> 01:09:16.205
