I have to go back to New York.

1534
01:09:32.333 --> 01:09:34.463
[Henry] Ah. watch out!
Whoosh! I'm falling!

1535
01:09:36.958 --> 01:09:39.788
You didn't catch me.

1536
01:09:42.708 --> 01:09:43.538
