like we talked about.

1542
01:09:56.583 --> 01:09:59.133
we both decided not to be together
no matter where we are.

1543
01:09:59.208 --> 01:10:00.828
but we both want to be with you.

1544
01:10:01.666 --> 01:10:04.036
But you're not near me
if you're in New York.

1545
01:10:04.583 --> 01:10:06.423
Well. we all still live in New York.

1546
01:10:07.083 --> 01:10:08.923
Yeah. but I go to school here.

1547
01:10:09.583 --> 01:10:10.633
Just for right now.

1548
01:10:11.541 --> 01:10:13.921
Like that time we were in Copenhagen
for my play.

1549
01:10:14.000 --> 01:10:16.420
Remember all those kids in buckets?
[laughs]

1550
01:10:16.500 --> 01:10:17.670
I like my school here.

1551
01:10:17.750 --> 01:10:20.290
and Mom says we could stay here
if we want.

1552
