- Yeah.

2784
02:10:38.166 --> 02:10:40.246
- [Charlie] All right. Thank you.
- [Carter] Take care.

2785
02:10:44.541 --> 02:10:47.501
We were going to bring him to dinner.
but he's so wiped out.

2786
02:10:47.583 --> 02:10:48.673
You want to take him?

2787
02:10:50.083 --> 02:10:52.043
- It's your night.
- I know.

2788
02:10:52.125 --> 02:10:53.995
- Yeah. I'll drop him back in the morning.
- Good.

2789
02:10:54.083 --> 02:10:56.253
Yeah. text me when you're up.
We'll figure something out.

2790
02:10:56.333 --> 02:10:58.173
You're going to go with your dad. okay?

2791
02:10:58.250 --> 02:10:59.420
- Okay.
- [Nicole] Yeah?

2792
02:11:10.500 --> 02:11:12.080
